re set to take over not just the White House, but every lever of power in t=
he city. <strong>Donald</strong> <strong>Trump</strong> is returning to off=
ice with more public goodwill than ever. Democrats, meanwhile, are going on=
 television reciting talking points about how they didn=E2=80=99t lose as b=
adly as they could have. It=E2=80=99s depressing, but what else is there to=
 say? At least it=E2=80=99s the holidays. =E2=80=99Tis the season for banal=
 pleasantries,
beef tenderloin, drone sightings, and belts of champagne to dull the pain.<=
/p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;=
margin-bottom:0px;">At a holiday reception for the Democratic National Comm=
ittee on Sunday night at the Willard, just steps from the White House, <str=
ong>President</strong> <strong>Biden</strong> acknowledged his party=E2=80=
=99s plight with predictable garbled bromides, thanking supporters for thei=
r work and urging them to keep fighting. =E2=80=9CWhile our time in
office is coming to an end, the America of our dreams is calling us to stay=
 engaged,=E2=80=9D Biden said, flanked by his wife, <strong>Jill</strong>; =
Vice President<strong> Kamala Harris</strong>; and her husband, <strong>Dou=
g Emhoff</strong>. =E2=80=9CWe just have to remember=E2=80=94you=E2=80=99ve=
 heard me say it a thousand times=E2=80=94remember who we are: We=E2=80=99r=
e the United States of America, for God=E2=80=99s sake!=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p><=
p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">Bi=
den wouldn=E2=80=99t take any blame
for the party=E2=80=99s defeat, of course. He said the electorate just didn=
=E2=80=99t understand his accomplishments. =E2=80=9CFolks, look, all the th=
ings we passed=E2=80=94we knew people weren=E2=80=99t going to see it,=E2=
=80=9D Biden told the crowd. =E2=80=9CBillions of dollars being invested. I=
t just takes time to get it built. It takes time to get it going. It=E2=80=
=99s not going to happen for another five, six months, in many places. It=
=E2=80=99s just getting started.=E2=80=9D One day, <em>surely</em>, the vot=
ers will finally get it.=C2=A0</p></div>
